WikimediaEditorTasksEnabledCounters.description:
Counter classes to enable, with associated configuration. Fields:\n* class: the fully qualified class name\n* counter_key: the count property name associated with the counter, for storing in the DB and surfacing in the MediaWiki API

Example:
{
	"class": "MediaWiki\Extension\WikimediaEditorTasks\WikipediaAppDescriptionEditCounter",
	"counter_key": "app_description_edits",
	}
